Simple prep-time limitations. If you can choose between having a factory back 
home chunk out nukes while you use the last batch, or having to find and rig 
an appropriate rock onsite, you go for the factory. It doesn\'t take the guys 
in the field hardly any time at all to just push launch buttons...

GC
